# Ability Name		Unique Key							Source Page		Category of Ability	Type																					Required Ability																									Required Class		Required Non-Monster Lvl	Required Text								Var. Min. Value				Description
Acute Vision		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Acute Vision			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01																																									PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,1	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1																			DESC:When you are raging, your visual senses improve, granting you darkvision.
Moment Of Clarity		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Moment Of Clarity		SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01.one-action.CONCENTRATE.RAGE																																				PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,1	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1																			DESC:You push back your rage for a moment in order to think clearly. Until the end of this turn, you can use actions with the concentrate trait even if those actions don't have the rage trait.
Raging Intimidation	KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Raging Intimidation		SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01																																									PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,1	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1																			DESC:Your fury fills your foes with fear. While you are raging, your Demoralize and Scare to Death actions (from the Intimidation skill and an Intimidation skill feat, respectively) gain the rage trait, allowing you to use them while raging. As soon as you meet the prerequisites for the skill feats Intimidating Glare and Scare to Death, you gain these feats.
Raging Thrower		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Raging Thrower			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01.BARBARIAN																																																																DESC:Thrown weapons become especially deadly in your fury. You apply the additional damage from Rage to your thrown weapon attacks. If you have the Brutal Critical feat or the devastator class feature, apply their benefits to thrown weapon attacks.
Sudden Charge		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Sudden Charge			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01.two-actions.FLOURISH.OPEN																																					PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,1	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1																			DESC:With a quick sprint, you dash up to your foe and swing. Stride twice. If you end your movement within melee reach of at least one enemy, you can make a melee Strike against that enemy. You can use Sudden Charge while Burrowing, Climbing, Flying, or Swimming instead of Striding if you have the corresponding movement type.
Acute Scent			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Acute Scent			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02																																									PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,2	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2			PRETEXT:Prerequisites Acute Vision or darkvision								DESC:When you Rage, your sense of smell improves. You gain imprecise scent with a range of 30 feet.
Furious Finish		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Furious Finish			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.one-action.rage																																						PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,2	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2																			DESC:Desperate to finish the fight, you pour all your rage into one final blow. Make a Strike. If it hits, you gain a circumstance bonus to damage equal to the number of rounds remaining in your Rage (maximum 10). After this Strike, your Rage immediately ends, and you are fatigued until you rest for at least 10 minutes.
No Escape			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ No Escape			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.reaction.rage																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,2	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2																			DESC:TRIGGER - A foe within reach attempts to move away from you.	DESC:You keep pace with a retreating foe. Stride up to your Speed, following the foe and keeping it in reach throughout its movement until it stops moving or you've moved your full Speed. You can use No Escape to Burrow, Climb, Fly, or Swim instead of Stride if you have the corresponding movement type.
Second Wind			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Second Wind			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.reaction.rage																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,2	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2																			DESC:You can enter a second rage, but afterward you need to catch your breath. You can Rage without waiting for 1 minute after the previous Rage (or 1 round, with quick rage), but when you end this second Rage, you're fatigued until you rest for 10 minutes.
Shake It Off		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Shake It Off			SOURCEPAGE:p.88	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.one-action.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.RAGE																																																												DESC:You concentrate on your rage, overcoming fear and fighting back sickness. Reduce your frightened condition value by 1, and attempt a Fortitude save to recover from the sickened condition as if you had spent an action retching; you reduce your sickened condition value by 1 on a failure (but not on a critical failure), by 2 on a success, or by 3 on a critical success.
Fast Movement		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Fast Movement			SOURCEPAGE:p.89	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04																																									PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,4	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4																			DESC:Your rage is a frenzy of rapid movements. While you are raging, you gain a +10-foot status bonus to your Speed.
Raging Athlete		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Raging Athlete			SOURCEPAGE:p.89	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04																																									PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,4	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4			PRETEXT:Prerequisites expert in Athletics				PREVARGTEQ:PROF_Rank_Athletics,2	DESC:Physical obstacles can't hold back your fury. While you are raging, you gain a climb Speed and swim Speed equal to your land Speed, the DC of High Jumps and Long Jumps decreases by 10, and your Leap distance increases by 5 feet when you jump horizontally and by 2 feet when you jump vertically.
Swipe				KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Swipe				SOURCEPAGE:p.89	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04.Action.two-actions.FLOURISH																																				PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,4	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4																			DESC:You make a wide, arcing swing. Make a single melee Strike and compare the attack roll result to the ACs of up to two foes, each of whom must be within your melee reach and adjacent to the other. Roll damage only once and apply it to each creature you hit. A Swipe counts as two attacks for your multiple attack penalty. If you're using a weapon with the sweep trait, its modifier applies to all your Swipe attacks.
Wounded Rage		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Wounded Rage			SOURCEPAGE:p.90	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04.reaction.BARBARIAN.RAGE																																					PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,4	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4																			DESC:Trigger - You take damage and are capable of entering a rage. You roar in pain, awakening the rage within you. You Rage.
Animal Skin			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Animal Skin			SOURCEPAGE:p.90	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.BARBARIAN.INSTINCT.MORPH.PRIMAL.TRANSMUTATION						PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Animal Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,6	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6			PRETEXT:Prerequisites animal instinct										DESC:Your proficiency in unarmored defense increases to expert. While you are raging and unarmored, your skin transforms into a thick hide resembling your animal's skin. You gain a +1 status bonus to AC instead of taking a -1 penalty to AC; if you have the greater juggernaut class feature, this status bonus increases to +2. The thickness of your hide gives you a Dexterity modifier cap to your AC of +3.
Attack Of Opportunity	KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Attack Of Opportunity	SOURCEPAGE:p.90	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.BARBARIAN																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,6	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6																			DESC:Trigger A creature within your reach uses a manipulate action or a move action, makes a ranged attack, or leaves a square during a move action it's using.&nl;You swat a foe that leaves an opening. Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature. If your attack is a critical hit and the trigger was a manipulate action, you disrupt that action. This Strike doesn't count toward your multiple attack penalty, and your multiple attack penalty doesn't apply to this Strike.
Brutal Bully		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Brutal Bully			SOURCEPAGE:p.90	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.BARBARIAN																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,6	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6			PRETEXT:Prerequisites expert in Athletics				PREVARGTEQ:Prof_Rank_Athletics,2	DESC:You push your foes around and leave bruises. While raging, when you successfully Disarm, Grapple, Shove, or Trip a foe, you deal that foe bludgeoning damage equal to your Strength modifier; add this to the damage from a critical success to Trip.
Cleave			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Cleave				SOURCEPAGE:p.90	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.Barbarian.Rage.reaction																																					PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,6	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6																			DESC:Trigger Your melee Strike kills a creature or knocks it unconscious, and another foe is adjacent to that creature. You swing clear through one foe and into another. Make a melee Strike against the second foe.
Dragon's Rage Breath	KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Dragon's Rage Breath		SOURCEPAGE:p.90	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.Barbarian.action.two-actions.ARCANE.CONCENTRATE.EVOCATION.INSTINCT.RAGE		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Dragon Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,6	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6			PRETEXT:Prerequisites dragon instinct										DESC:Requirements - You haven't used this ability since you last Raged. &nl;You breathe deeply and exhale powerful energy in a 30-foot cone or 60-foot line, dealing 1d6 damage per level. The area and damage type match those of your dragon (see Table 3-4 on page 86). If you used this ability in the last hour, the area and the damage are halved (15-foot cone or 30-foot line; 1d6 damage for every 2 levels). Each creature in the area must attempt a basic Reflex save.
Giant's Stature		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Giant's Stature		SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.one-action.Barbarian											PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Giant Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,6	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6			PRETEXT:Prerequisites giant instinct										DESC:Requirements - You are Medium or smaller. You grow to incredible size. You become Large, increasing your reach by 5 feet and gaining the clumsy 1 condition (page 618) until you stop raging. Your equipment grows with you.
Spirits' Interference	KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Spirits' Interference	SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.one-action.Barbarian											PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Spirit Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,6	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6			PRETEXT:Prerequisites spirit instinct										DESC:You call forth protective spirits to ward off ranged attacks. Until your rage ends, anyone making a ranged attack against you must succeed at a DC 5 flat check or the attack misses with no effect.
Animal Rage			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Animal Rage			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08														PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Animal Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,8	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8			PRETEXT:Prerequisites animal instinct										DESC:You transform into your animal. You gain the effects of the 3rd-level animal form spell except you use your own statistics, temporary Hit Points, and unarmed attacks instead of those granted by animal form. You also retain the constant abilities of your gear. If your animal is a frog, your tongue's reach increases to 15 feet. Dismissing the transformation gains the rage trait.
Furious Bully		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Furious Bully			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.BARBARIAN																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,8	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8			PRETEXT:Prerequisites master in Athletics				PREVARGTEQ:Prof_Rank_Athletics,3	DESC:You bully foes across the battlefield. While raging, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks for attack actions.
Renewed Vigor		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Renewed Vigor			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.BARBARIAN.one-action.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.RAGE																																	PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,8	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8																			DESC:You pause to recover your raging vigor. You gain temporary Hit Points equal to half your level plus your Constitution modifier.
Share Rage			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Share Rage			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.BARBARIAN.one-action.AUDITORY.BARBARIAN.RAGE.VISUAL																																PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,8	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8																			DESC:Requirements You haven't used this ability since you last Raged. &nl;You stoke an ally's fury. While you are raging, one willing creature within 30 feet gains the effects of the Rage action, except it can still use concentrate actions.
Sudden Leap			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Sudden Leap			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.Barbarian																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,8	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8																			DESC:You swing at a foe while mid-leap. Make a Leap, High Jump, or Long Jump and attempt one melee Strike at any point during your jump. Immediately after the Strike, you fall to the ground if you're in the air, even if you haven't reached the maximum distance of your jump. If the distance you fall is no more than the height of your jump, you take no damage and land upright. When attempting a High Jump or Long Jump during a Sudden Leap, determine the DC using the Long Jump DCs, and increase your maximum distance to double your Speed.
Thrash			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Thrash				SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.one-action.FEAT 8.BARBARIAN.RAGE																																				PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,8	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8																			DESC:Requirements You have a foe grabbed. &nl;You thrash the grabbed foe around. It takes bludgeoning damage equal to your Strength modifier plus your ferocious specialization damage plus your Rage damage. The foe must attempt a basic Fortitude save against your class DC.
Come And Get Me		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Come And Get Me		SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.Feat 10.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.RAGE.one-action																																			PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,10	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=10																			DESC:You open yourself to attacks so you can respond in turn. Until your rage ends, you are flat-footed, and damage rolls against you gain a +2 circumstance bonus. If a creature hits you, that creature is flat-footed to you until the end of your next turn. If you hit it before the end of your next turn, you gain temporary Hit Points equal to your Constitution modifier, or double that on a critical hit. These temporary Hit Points last until the end of your rage.
Furious Sprint		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Furious Sprint			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.Feat 10.BARBARIAN.Rage.action.two-actions																																			PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,10	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=10																			DESC:You rush forward. Stride up to five times your Speed in a straight line. You can increase the number of actions this activity takes to 3 to Stride up to eight times your Speed in a straight line instead.
Great Cleave		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Great Cleave			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.Feat 10.BARBARIAN.Rage												PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Cleave																		PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,10	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=10			PRETEXT:Prerequisites Cleave												DESC:Your fury carries your weapon through multiple foes. When you Cleave, if your Strike also kills or knocks the target unconscious, you can continue to make melee Strikes until you make a Strike that doesn't kill or knock a creature unconscious, or until there are no creatures adjacent to the most recent creature you attacked while Cleaving, whichever comes first.
Knockback			KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Knockback			SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.Feat 10.BARBARIAN.Rage																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,10	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=10																			DESC:Requirements Your last action was a successful Strike. The weight of your swing drives your enemy back. You push the foe back 5 feet, with the effects of a successful Shove. You can follow the foe as normal for a successful Shove.
Terrifying Howl		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Terrifying Howl		SOURCEPAGE:p.91	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.Feat 10.BARBARIAN.Rage.AUDITORY										PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Intimidating Glare																PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,10	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=10			PRETEXT:Prerequisites Intimidating Glare										DESC:You unleash a terrifying howl. Attempt Intimidate checks to Demoralize each creature within 30 feet. Regardless of the results of your checks, each creature is then temporarily immune to Terrifying Howl for 1 minute.
Dragon's Rage Wings	KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Dragon's Rage Wings		SOURCEPAGE:p.92	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 12.one-action.BARBARIAN.INSTINCT.MORPH.PRIMAL.RAGE.TRANSMUTATION				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Dragon Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,12	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=12			PRETEXT:Prerequisites dragon instinct										DESC:You sprout dragon wings from your back of the same color as your chosen dragon. While you are raging, you gain a fly Speed equal to your land Speed. If you are flying when your rage ends, you start to fall but the transformation only completes at the last moment, so you take no damage from the fall and land standing up.
Furious Grab		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Furious Grab			SOURCEPAGE:p.92	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 12.one-action.BARBARIAN.RAGE																																					PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,12	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=12																			DESC:Requirements Your last action was a successful Strike, and either you have a hand free or your Strike used a grapple weapon.&nl; You grab your foe while it's distracted by your attack. The foe you hit becomes grabbed, as if you had succeeded at an Athletics check to Grapple the foe.
Predator's Pounce		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Predator's Pounce		SOURCEPAGE:p.92	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 12.one-action.BARBARIAN.FLOURISH.INSTINCT.OPEN.RAGE						PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Animal Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,12	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=12			PRETEXT:Prerequisites animal instinct										DESC:Requirements You are unarmored or wearing light armor.&nl;You close the distance to your prey in a blur, pouncing on the creature before it can react. You Stride up to your Speed and make a Strike at the end of your movement.
Spirit's Wrath		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Spirit's Wrath			SOURCEPAGE:p.92	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 12.one-action.ATTACK.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.INSTINCT.RAGE					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Spirit Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,12	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=12			PRETEXT:Prerequisites spirit instinct										DESC:You call forth an ephemeral apparition, typically the ghost of an ancestor or a nature spirit, which takes the form of a wisp. The spirit wisp makes a melee wisp rush unarmed attack against an enemy within 120 feet of you. The wisp's attack modifier is equal to your proficiency bonus for martial weapons plus your Strength modifier plus a +2 item bonus, and it applies the same circumstance and status bonuses and penalties that you have. On a hit, the wisp deals damage equal to 4d8 plus your Constitution modifier. The damage is your choice of negative or positive damage; don't apply your Rage damage or your weapon specialization damage, but circumstance and status bonuses and penalties that would also affect the wisp's damage apply. If your wisp's Strike is a critical hit, the target becomes frightened 1. This attack uses and counts toward your multiple attack penalty as if you were the one attacking.
Titan's Stature		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Titan's Stature		SOURCEPAGE:p.92	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 12.BARBARIAN.INSTINCT.POLYMORPH.TRANSMUTATION							PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Giant Instinct	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Giant's Stature		PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,12	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=12			PRETEXT:Prerequisites giant instinct, Giant's Stature								DESC:You grow to even greater size. When using Giant's Stature, you can instead become Huge (increasing your reach by 10 feet if you were Medium or smaller) while you are raging. You have the clumsy 1 condition (page 618) as long as you are Huge.
Awesome Blow		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Awesome Blow			SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 14.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.RAGE										PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Knockback																		PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,14	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=14			PRETEXT:Prerequisites Knockback											DESC:Your attacks are so powerful, they can flatten your opponents. When you use Knockback, you can attempt an Athletics check against your target's Fortitude DC. &nl;Critical Success You gain the critical success effect of a Shove, then the critical success effect of a Trip against the target. &nl;Success You gain the success effect of a Shove, then the success effect of a Trip against the target.&nl;Failure You gain the normal effect of Knockback.
Giant's Lunge		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Giant's Lunge			SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 14.one-action.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.INSTINCT.RAGE						PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Giant Instinct													PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,14	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=14			PRETEXT:Prerequisites giant instinct										DESC:You extend your body and prepare to attack foes outside your normal reach. Until your rage ends, all your melee weapons and unarmed attacks gain reach 10. This doesn't increase the reach of any weapon or unarmed attack that already has the reach trait, but it does combine with abilities that increase your reach due to increased size, such as Giant's Stature.
Vengeful Strike		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Vengeful Strike		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 14.reaction.BARBARIAN.RAGE										PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Come and Get Me																	PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,14	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=14			PRETEXT:Prerequisites Come and Get Me										DESC:Trigger A creature within your reach succeeds or critically succeeds at an attack against you.&nl;Requirements You're under the effect of Come and Get Me.&nl;When struck by an enemy, you respond in turn. Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature. This Strike doesn't count toward your multiple attack penalty, and your multiple attack penalty doesn't apply to this Strike.
Whirlwind Strike		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Whirlwind Strike		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 14.three-action.three-actions.BARBARIAN.FLOURISH.OPEN																																	PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,14	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=14																			DESC:You attack all nearby adversaries. Make a melee Strike against each enemy within your melee reach. Each attack counts toward your multiple attack penalty, but do not increase your penalty until you have made all your attacks.
Collateral Thrash		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Collateral Thrash		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 16.BARBARIAN.RAGE												PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Thrash																		PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,16	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=16			PRETEXT:Prerequisites Thrash												DESC:When you Thrash a grabbed foe, you smack that foe into another nearby. Another foe adjacent to the grabbed foe also takes your Thrash damage, with a basic Reflex save against your class DC.
Dragon Transformation	KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Dragon Transformation	SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 16.one-action.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.INSTINCT.POLYMORPH.PRIMAL.RAGE.TRANSMUTATION	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Barbarian Class Feature ~ Instinct ~ Dragon Instinct	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Dragon's Rage Wings	PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,16	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=16			PRETEXT:Prerequisites dragon instinct, Dragon's Rage Wings							DESC:You transform into a ferocious Large dragon, gaining the effects of 6th-level dragon form except that you use your own AC and attack modifier; you also apply your extra damage from Rage. The action to Dismiss the transformation gains the rage trait. At 18th level, you gain a +20-foot status bonus to your fly Speed, your damage bonus with dragon Strikes increases to +12, your breath weapon DC increases to 30, and you gain a +14 status bonus to your breath weapon damage.
Reckless Abandon		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Reckless Abandon		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 16.free-action.BARBARIAN.RAGE																																					PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,16	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=16																			DESC:Trigger Your turn begins, and you are at half or fewer Hit Points. &nl;Your blood boils when you take a beating, and you throw caution to the wind to finish the fight. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to attack rolls, a -2 penalty to AC, and a -1 penalty to saves. These bonuses and penalties last until your Rage ends or until you are above half Hit Points, whichever comes first.
Brutal Critical		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Brutal Critical		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 18.BARBARIAN																																							PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,18	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=18																			DESC:Your critical hits are particularly devastating. On a critical hit, add one extra damage die. This is in addition to any extra dice you gain if the weapon is deadly or fatal. The target also takes persistent bleed damage equal to two damage dice.
Perfect Clarity		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Perfect Clarity		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 18.reaction.BARBARIAN.CONCENTRATE.FORTUNE.RAGE																																		PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,18	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=18																			DESC:Trigger You fail or critically fail an attack roll or Will save.&nl;You burn out all of your rage to ensure that your attack lands and your mind remains free. Reroll the triggering attack roll or Will save with a +2 circumstance bonus, use the better result,and resolve the effect. You then immediately stop raging.
Vicious Evisceration	KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Vicious Evisceration		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 18.two-action.two-actions.BARBARIAN.RAGE																																			PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,18	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=18																			DESC:You make a vicious attack that maims your enemy. Make a melee Strike. If the Strike hits and deals damage, the target is drained 1, or drained 2 on a critical success.
Contagious Rage		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Contagious Rage		SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 20.AUDITORY.BARBARIAN.RAGE.VISUAL									PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feat,Barbarian Feat ~ Share Rage																	PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,20	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=20			PRETEXT:Prerequisites Share Rage											DESC:You can drive your allies into a frenzy, granting them incredible benefits. You can ignore the requirements on Share Rage, using it multiple times in a Rage. Allies affected by Share Rage who accept your anathema for the duration of the Rage gain your instinct ability and the specialization ability it gains from weapon specialization, but not greater weapon specialization.
Quaking Stomp		KEY:Barbarian Feat ~ Quaking Stomp			SOURCEPAGE:p.93	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 20.one-action.BARBARIAN.MANIPULATE.RAGE																																			PREVARGTEQ:BarbarianCL,20	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=20																			DESC:Frequency once per 10 minutes&nl;You stomp the ground with such force that it creates a minor earthquake, with the effects of the earthquake spell.

