Bardic Lore						KEY:Bard Feat ~ Bardic Lore			SOURCEPAGE:p.99	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01.BARD								PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Bard Class Feature ~ Muses ~ Enigma											PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,01																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1			PRETEXT:Prerequisites enigma muse															DESC:Your studies make you informed on every subject. You are trained in Bardic Lore, a special Lore skill that can be used only to Recall Knowledge, but on any topic. If you have legendary proficiency in Occultism, you gain expert proficiency in Bardic Lore, but you can't increase your proficiency rank in Bardic Lore by any other means.
Lingering Composition				KEY:Bard Feat ~ Lingering Composition	SOURCEPAGE:p.99	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01.BARD								PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,Bard Class Feature ~ Muses ~ Maestro	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,TYPE.Focus Pool	PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,01																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1			PRETEXT:Prerequisites maestro muse, focus pool													DESC:By adding a flourish, you make your compositions last longer. You learn the lingering composition focus spell (page 387). Increase the number of Focus Points in your focus pool by 1.																																																																																																										BONUS:VAR|FocusPool|1
Reach Spell						KEY:Bard Feat ~ Reach Spell			SOURCEPAGE:p.99	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01.one-action.BARD.CONCENTRATE.METAMAGIC																									PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,01																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1																							DESC:You can extend your spells' range. If the next action you use is to Cast a Spell that has a range, increase that spell's range by 30 feet. As is standard for increasing spell ranges, if the spell normally has a range of touch, you extend its range to 30 feet.
Versatile Performance				KEY:Bard Feat ~ Versatile Performance	SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 01.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,01	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,PolymathMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1			PRETEXT:Prerequisites polymath muse															DESC:[Not Implemented currently!]You can rely on the grandeur of your performances rather than ordinary social skills. You can use Performance instead of Diplomacy to Make an Impression and instead of Intimidation to Demoralize. You can also use an acting Performance instead of Deception to Impersonate. You can use your proficiency rank in Performance to meet the requirements of skill feats that require a particular rank in Deception, Diplomacy, or Intimidation.
Cantrip Expansion					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Cantrip Expansion		SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,02																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2																							DESC:Study broadens your range of simple spells. Add two additional cantrips from your spell list to your repertoire.																																																																																																															BONUS:SPELLKNOWN|CLASS=Bard;LEVEL=0|2
Esoteric Polymath					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Esoteric Polymath		SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,02	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,PolymathMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2			PRETEXT:Prerequisites polymath muse															DESC:You keep a book of occult spells, similar to a wizard's spellbook, and can use its spells to supplement your spell repertoire. Add all the spells in your repertoire to this book for free. You can use the Occultism skill to Learn Spells (page 238) and add them to your spellbook by paying the appropriate cost, similar to a wizard. During your daily preparations, choose any one spell from your book of occult spells. If that spell is already in your spell repertoire, you can treat it as an additional signature spell that day. If it isn't in your repertoire, treat it as though it were until your next daily preparations.
Inspire Competence				KEY:Bard Feat ~ Inspire Competence		SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,02	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,MaestroMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2			PRETEXT:Prerequisites maestro muse															DESC:You learn the inspire competence composition cantrip (page 386), which aids your allies' skills.																																																																																																																													SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Bard=0|Inspire Competence
Loremaster's Etude				KEY:Bard Feat ~ Loremaster's Etude		SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.BARD.FORTUNE							PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,TYPE.Focus Pool														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,02	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,EnigmaMuse=true																				PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2			PRETEXT:Prerequisites enigma muse, focus pool													DESC:You magically unlock memories, making them easier to recall. You learn the loremaster's etude composition spell (page 387). Increase the number of Focus Points in your focus pool by 1.																																																																																																										BONUS:VAR|FocusPool|1	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Bard=1|Loremaster's Etude
Multifarious Muse					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Multifarious Muse		SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 02.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,02																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=2																							DESC:Your muse doesn't fall into a single label. Choose a type of muse other than that of your own. You gain a 1st-level feat that requires that muse, and your muse is now also a muse of that type, allowing you to take feats with the other muse as a prerequisite. You don't gain any of the other effects of the muse you chose. Special You can take this feat multiple times. Each time you do, you must choose a different type of muse other than that of your own.																																											STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:ABILITY|Class Feature|TYPE=Muses
Inspire Defense					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Inspire Defense		SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,04	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,MaestroMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4			PRETEXT:Prerequisites maestro muse															DESC:You learn the inspire defense composition cantrip (page 386), which protects you and allies.																																																																																																																													SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Bard=0|Inspire Defense
Melodious Spell					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Melodious Spell		SOURCEPAGE:p.101	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04.one-action.BARD.CONCENTRATE.MANIPULATE.METAMAGIC																							PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,04																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4																							DESC:You subtly weave your spellcasting into your performance. If the next action you take is to Cast a Spell, attempt a Performance check against all observers' Perception DCs. If your Performance check is successful against an observer's Perception DC, that observer doesn't notice that you are Casting a Spell, even though normally spells have sensory manifestations that would make spellcasting obvious to those around you, and verbal, somatic, and material components are extremely overt. You hide all of these as part of an ordinary performance. This hides only the spell's spellcasting actions and manifestations, not its effects, so an observer might still see a ray streak out from you or see you vanish.
Triple Time						KEY:Bard Feat ~ Triple Time			SOURCEPAGE:p.101	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,04																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4																							DESC:You learn the triple time composition cantrip (page 387), which speeds up you and your allies for a round.																																																																																																																											SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Bard=0|Triple Time
Versatile Signature				KEY:Bard Feat ~ Versatile Signature		SOURCEPAGE:p.101	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 04.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,04	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,PolymathMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=4			PRETEXT:Prerequisites polymath muse															DESC:While most bards are known for certain signature performances and spells, you're always tweaking your available repertoire. When you make your daily preparations, you can change one of your signature spells to a different spell of that level from your repertoire.
Dirge Of Doom					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Dirge Of Doom			SOURCEPAGE:p.101	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,06																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6																							DESC:You learn the dirge of doom composition cantrip (page 386), which frightens your enemies.																																																																																																																														SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Bard=0|Dirge Of Doom
Harmonize						KEY:Bard Feat ~ Harmonize			SOURCEPAGE:p.101	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.one-action.BARD.CONCENTRATE.MANIPULATE.METAMAGIC																							PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,06	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,MaestroMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6			PRETEXT:Prerequisites maestro muse															DESC:You can perform multiple compositions simultaneously. If your next action is to cast a composition, it becomes a harmonized composition. Unlike a normal composition, a harmonized composition doesn't end if you cast another composition, and you can cast another composition on the same turn as a harmonized one. Casting another harmonized composition ends any harmonized composition you have in effect.
Steady Spellcasting				KEY:Bard Feat ~ Steady Spellcasting		SOURCEPAGE:p.101	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 06.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,06																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6																							DESC:You don't lose spells easily. If a reaction would disrupt your spellcasting action, attempt a DC 15 flat check. If you succeed, your action isn't disrupted.
Eclectic Skill					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Eclectic Skill		SOURCEPAGE:p.101	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,08	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,PolymathMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8			PRETEXT:Prerequisites polymath muse, master in Occultism					PREVARGTEQ:Prof_Rank_Occultism,3	DESC:Your broad experiences translate to a range of skills. You add your level to all skill checks in which you are untrained. You can attempt any skill check that normally requires you to be trained, even if you are untrained. If you have legendary proficiency in Occultism, you can attempt any skill check that normally requires you to have expert proficiency, even if untrained or trained.
Inspire Heroics					KEY:Bard Feat ~ Inspire Heroics		SOURCEPAGE:p.102	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.BARD								PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Class Feature,TYPE.Focus Pool														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,08	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,MaestroMuse=true																			PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8			PRETEXT:Prerequisites maestro muse, focus pool													DESC:Your performances inspire even greater deeds in your allies. You learn the inspire heroics metamagic focus spell (page 387). Increase the number of Focus Points in your focus pool by 1.																																																																																																										BONUS:VAR|FocusPool|1	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Bard=0|Inspire Heroics
Know-It-All						KEY:Bard Feat ~ Know-It-All			SOURCEPAGE:p.102	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 08.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,08	PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,enigmaMuse=true																				PREPCLEVEL:MIN=8			PRETEXT:Prerequisites enigma muse															DESC:When you succeed at a Knowledge check, you gain additional information or context. When you critically succeed at a Knowledge check, at the GM's discretion you might gain even more additional information or context than normal.
House Of Imaginary Walls			KEY:Bard Feat ~ House Of Imaginary Walls	SOURCEPAGE:p.102	CATEGORY:CLASS FEAT	TYPE:Bard Class Feat.Class Feat.FEAT 10.BARD																														PREVARGTEQ:BardCL,10																										PREPCLEVEL:MIN=10																							DESC:You erect an imaginary barrier others believe to be real. You learn the house of imaginary walls composition cantrip (page 386).
